'''Lord Dalton Piscarilius''' was the leader of [[Port Piscarilius|Piscarilius]] until his death during a fishing trip.{{CiteNPC|npc=Lady Shauna Piscarilius|quote=I was born into the Piscarilius House as the only child of Lord Dalton Piscarilius. After my fool of a father got himself killed on a fishing trip, leadership fell to me.|name=Death}} His only daughter, [[Lady Shauna Piscarilius]], succeeded him as leader of Piscarilius.{{NamedRef|Death}}

Lady Shauna describes him as a man only interested in his own wealth, ignorant of the struggles of his own people.{{CiteNPC|npc=Lady Shauna Piscarilius|quote=My father never cared about anyone. He was far more interested in increasing his own wealth at the cost of his people.}}

{{Succession|predecessor=Eventually [[Lord Piscarilius II]]|title=Leader of [[Port Piscarilius|Piscarilius]]|successor=[[Lady Shauna Piscarilius]]}}

